SECTION - 14

DETACHED HEAD 

- > Commits made in detached HEad state will be garbage collected.

git checkout <SHA1> 
    - > The HEAD now points to a specific commit.


- > By default, unreachable Git Objects are garbage collected after 30 days.
- > If one is happy with the commits made in the detached head state - keep them by creation of the new branch using command 
    - > git checkout -b <branch name>
    

